BE is the most commonly prefered course after MPC across India
After completion of your BE ,You can choose any of the below as your career option:


IES exam--Jobs in public sector and railway
Jobs based on your respective branches in BE
Merchant Navy--Marine engineer
 ME
 Defence entrance--Indian NAVY,AIRFORCE,ARMY
 MBA
 MS in Foreign Universities
 UPSC--IAS,Indian class 1 officers
 